# Tech Stack Lock

## Locked Decisions

| Decision | Locked To | Do NOT Switch To |
|----------|-----------|------------------|
| Game Engine | Unity 2021.3 | Unity 2022+, Godot, Unreal |
| Language | C# | Other languages |
| Board SDK | fun.board 3.2.1 | Other versions without verification |
| Piece Set | Arcade pieces | Strata blocks, custom pieces |
| Interaction Log | CSV, local file | JSON, cloud DB, binary |
| Log Fields | timestamp, session_id, player_id, piece_id, action, position, rotation, game_state | Fewer fields; different schema |
| Domain | Coding (logic puzzles) | Math, Reading |

## Adding Dependencies

1. Check Board SDK compatibility (Unity 2021.3, Input System 1.7.0).
2. Document in TECH_STACK.md.
3. Update this rule if it affects locked decisions.

## Migration Notes

- Upgrading Unity: Board SDK must support new version first.
- Upgrading Board SDK: Test piece events, Session API; check changelog at docs.dev.board.fun.
